Compiling and installing ubuntu package:

git clone git://github.com/qoyllur/atkbd-front.git
cd atkbd-front
dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot
cd ..
sudo dkpg -i atkbd-front-source*deb
mkdir tmp
m-a -u test build atkbd-front-source

Then install atkbd-front-utils and atkbd-front-modules.

Usage:
/etc/init.d/atkbd-front start|stop

